Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:02.34,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}《终空》前情提要\N{\fs40\b0}Previously on "Final Space,"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.37,0:00:03.80,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞在内空见到了波罗\N{\fs40\b0}Gary journeys to Inner Space to see the Titan,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:05.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一个已经沉睡了一万年的泰坦\N{\fs40\b0}Bolo, who's been asleep for 10,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.64,0:00:08.07,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在内空中  盖瑞的父亲派他去地球\N{\fs40\b0}While there, Gary's father tells him to go to Earth
