Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:12.01,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}借助那个炸弹  他们就能封锁终空\N{\fs40\b0}With it, they can close Final Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.04,0:00:13.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}让我们祈祷时间还够用吧\N{\fs40\b0}Let's hope there's still time.
