Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.31,0:00:24.21,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  还有1分钟  饼干就烤好了\N{\fs40\b0}Gary. The cookies will be done in one minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.24,0:00:28.95,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好极了  我真的好激动啊...\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, good. I'm extremely excited...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:32.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}有饼干诶\N{\fs40\b0}for these cookies.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.11,0:00:33.81,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我好害怕  HUE\N{\fs40\b0}I'm scared, H.U.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.81,0:00:34.98,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我知道  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}I know, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:36.89,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你会一直陪我到最后吗？\N{\fs40\b0}You'll stay with me till the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:39.82,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我会一直陪你  直到最后的最后\N{\fs40\b0}Till the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:42.63,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}谢谢你  HUE\N{\fs40\b0}Thank you, H.U.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:45.60,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我很荣幸  能做你的朋友\N{\fs40\b0} It's been an honor to be your friend.
