Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:20.86,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  能精确转述一下你爸的指示吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, what were your father's exact instructions?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.87,0:01:24.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他说  “找到反物质炸弹  然后用它修补缺口”\N{\fs40\b0}He said, "Get the anti-matter bomb and close the breach."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.03,0:01:26.54,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他说地球上的那个炸弹在哪了吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Did he say where on Earth the bomb is?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.57,0:01:29.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}在纽约  地球上那个纽约\N{\fs40\b0}In New York. The one on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:30.64,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}纽约是个很大的地方\N{\fs40\b0}That's a really big place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.64,0:01:32.81,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  我说不定能帮到你\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, I might be able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.84,0:01:34.95,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我在你父亲的文件里找到了这个\N{\fs40\b0}I have found this in your father's files.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.98,0:01:40.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}日志2845B...  约翰·古茨比德舰长\N{\fs40\b0}Log 2845B ... Captain John Goodspeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:43.39,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}真是个重大的日子  经过这么长时间  我们终于做到了\N{\fs40\b0}Big day. Took forever, but we finally got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:47.96,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}是反物质炸弹\N{\fs40\b0}The anti-matter bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.99,0:01:49.59,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们在此所做的一切\N{\fs40\b0}What we do here could be the difference
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:51.06,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}关乎地球的幸存\N{\fs40\b0}between Earth's survival
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:53.43,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}抑或是  其于终空中的消亡\N{\fs40\b0}and its being swallowed up into Final Space.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:55.90,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}约翰  如果咱们做成了\N{\fs40\b0}Hey, John, if we survive this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.84,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}咱们就去吃顿墨西哥小卷饼庆功  你看怎么样？\N{\fs40\b0}what do you say we kick it up with some taquitos, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.93,0:01:59.84,DESC,,0,0,0,,{\be15}墨西哥小卷饼（Taquito）：一种墨西哥食品，由油炸玉米薄饼包裹牛肉、鸡肉、或奶酪馅制成。
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:02.37,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我要杀了他\N{\fs40\b0}I'm going to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:05.44,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我知道这是哪  就在无疆守卫的塔尖上\N{\fs40\b0}I know where that is. It's the Infinity Guard Spire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:08.45,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}所以下一站... 就是那了！\N{\fs40\b0}Then next stop ... that place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:19.99,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦我的天哪！HUE  发生了什么？\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, my gosh! H.U.E., wh... what is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们在哪？！\N{\fs40\b0}Where are we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.02,0:02:21.92,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们在地球  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}Earth, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.93,0:02:25.53,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}它从坐标上偏离了  正被吸入缺口\N{\fs40\b0}It has shifted from its coordinates and is being sucked into the breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.56,0:02:27.53,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}最先被吸走的就是海水\N{\fs40\b0}The oceans are the first to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:30.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}天哪  要来真的了\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, my God. It's happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:32.60,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}都是KVN的错  去死吧  KVN  去死！\N{\fs40\b0}I blame KVN. Way to go, KVN. Way to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.61,0:02:34.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我已经表现得很好了！\N{\fs40\b0}I'm getting better!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.01,0:02:36.81,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你越来越烂了  越来越烂！打我那下很疼的！\N{\fs40\b0}You're getting worse. So much worse! It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.84,0:02:38.24,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}特别特别疼！\N{\fs40\b0}It hurts me physically!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.91,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}♪ 事情正在变好 ♪\N{\fs40\b0}♪ Things are getting better ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:43.08,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}♪ 层云渐开  阳光普照 ♪\N{\fs40\b0}♪ The sun is shining, the clouds are parting ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:47.02,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}♪ 这个家伙正在进步 ♪\N{\fs40\b0}♪ And this guy is making great striiides ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:49.09,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}一起来！你最棒  KVN\N{\fs40\b0}Sing with me! You're doing great, KVN.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.12,0:02:51.23,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}谢了！我最棒！\N{\fs40\b0}Thanks! I am doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:55.30,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 哦天哪！   - 这可和想象的不一样\N{\fs40\b0}- Oh, my God! - That's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.83,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 乌龟？！   - 还是个小乌龟呢\N{\fs40\b0}- Turtles?! - That's a little one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:02:59.20,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我的个老天爷哪！\N{\fs40\b0}Dear Heavenly Lightning Lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:01.97,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们被忍者神龟袭击了！\N{\fs40\b0}We're being attacked by Ninja Sea Turtles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.98,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}不  盖瑞  是我们游到一群海龟里了\N{\fs40\b0}No, Gary. But we have flown into a school of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.71,DESC,,0,0,0,,{\be15}School：双关语，既指“一群水生动物”，又指“学校”。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:07.71,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好的  至少它们还在上学\N{\fs40\b0}Good! They're still in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.74,0:03:09.71,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Chookity.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.74,0:03:12.91,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这可不对劲  这非常不对劲\N{\fs40\b0}This is so wrong. This is very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.45,0:03:17.85,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}纽约\N{\fs40\b0}New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:20.52,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}整个星球都快被遗弃了  盖瑞\N{\fs40\b0}The planet has been mostly abandoned, Gary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.53,0:03:24.26,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}看啊  我以前来过纽约\N{\fs40\b0}Look at this place. I've been to New York before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.29,0:03:26.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这个纽约...\N{\fs40\b0}And this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:30.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}这个纽约看上去比之前的好点  不过也没好太多\N{\fs40\b0}This looks better. Not by much.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.03,0:03:31.63,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  很不幸\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.63,0:03:35.81,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你只有六个小时去找反物质炸弹\N{\fs40\b0}You'll have six hours to locate the anti-matter bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:40.94,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}六小时后  你现在看到的都会消失了\N{\fs40\b0}After that, all of what you see now will be gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.48,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}无疆守卫背叛了人类\N{\fs40\b0}The Infinity Guard betrayed the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.42,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们站好边了  而我们选择另外一边\N{\fs40\b0}They chose their side, and we're on the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:55.36,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}他们将对我们毫不手软  因此我们对他们也要如此\N{\fs40\b0}They will show us no mercy, so I suggest we show them none.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.39,0:03:57.49,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}现在我们出发  去找炸弹吧\N{\fs40\b0}Now let's find that bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:04:00.16,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我不知道你到底在说些啥  不过...\N{\fs40\b0}I have no idea what you're talking about, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:04.67,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我  先  溜  了！一会见！\N{\fs40\b0}Count. Me. Out! Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.80,0:04:06.40,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}盖瑞  舰上机器人们\N{\fs40\b0}Gary, the S.A.M.E.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.40,0:04:08.77,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}翻新了等离子体炬和电磁炮\N{\fs40\b0}have retrofitted the plasma torches, rail guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.71,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}以及其它的维护设备\N{\fs40\b0}and other sundry maintenance equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.74,0:04:13.58,DIAT,,0,0,0,,{\be15}它们现在变成了威猛的超级武器\N{\fs40\b0}into heinous super weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.11,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好极了  HUE  天哪\N{\fs40\b0}Yes, H.U.E.! Good lord, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.14,0:04:17.61,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}你知道吗  你已经被我\N{\fs40\b0}Do you know what that makes you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.61,0:04:20.05,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}评为“本月之星”了！\N{\fs40\b0}That makes you Employee of the freaking Month.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.32,0:04:25.86,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩  我能问你点事吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Quinn, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.89,0:04:30.39,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 开火！   - 天啦噜  来得也太快了点！\N{\fs40\b0}- Fire! - Oh, my ... That came kinda fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.40,0:04:33.00,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}干掉他们  伙计们！\N{\fs40\b0}Take 'em out, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.43,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Cookity pok!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:40.94,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}冲啊  冲啊  哦！\N{\fs40\b0}Go, go, go, go! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:51.15,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩  我还没问完呢\N{\fs40\b0}Quinn, I still have that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.18,0:04:53.65,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}呀啊！\N{\fs40\b0}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:04:58.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}\N{\fs40\b0}Woop! Pah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:05:00.62,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}上啊 月饼！\N{\fs40\b0}Go, Mooncake!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.63,0:05:03.86,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}好的好的好的！哦  不！\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, oh, yes! Yes! Oh, my ... oh, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:09.17,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}奎恩！还是那个问题\N{\fs40\b0}Quinn! About that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.20,0:05:10.53,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我想问的是  你愿意\N{\fs40\b0}What I wanted to ask is would you like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.53,0:05:13.97,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}和我一起喝一杯酒吗？\N{\fs40\b0}to drink alcoholic liquids out of a cup with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.97,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}现在？你非得现在问我？\N{\fs40\b0}Now? You're asking me this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.98,0:05:21.07,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦  成吧  然后你一个跟头就溜了\N{\fs40\b0}Oh, okay, just gonna cartwheel away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.45,0:05:26.18,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}哦差点！哦我的天哪！哦！\N{\fs40\b0}Okay, that was close! Oh, my God. Ow, ohh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:29.19,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}但是  我... 奎恩！\N{\fs40\b0}But just, you know, I mean... come on, Quinn!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.22,0:05:31.25,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}只是... 只是一杯酒而已\N{\fs40\b0}It jus... it's just a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.26,0:05:33.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我们难道不该专心一点吗？\N{\fs40\b0}Shouldn't we be concentrating on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.49,0:05:36.46,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}我专心不起来  因为我满脑子都是\N{\fs40\b0}I can't concentrate on this because all I am thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.49,0:05:38.76,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15} - 你想不想和我一起出去！   - 那就不想\N{\fs40\b0}- is if you wanna go out with me! - Then no.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.43,0:05:43.27,DIAB,,0,0,0,,{\be15}去死！去死！去死！为什么？\N{\fs40\b0}Die! Die! Die! Why?
